<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/19 (Thu) Actor-host Will Liu's Overnight Sensation/ Life in Taiwan: lunch box culture (Host: Gal)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=618&amp;p=641#p641"><![CDATA[
Actor-host Will Liu's Overnight Sensation/ Life in Taiwan: lunch box culture (Host: Gal)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I<br />Actor-host Will Liu banned from Douyin after his nipples were mistaken for breasts<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.straitstimes.com/life/entertainment/actor-host-will-liu-banned-from-douyin-after-his-nipples-were-mistaken-for-breasts">https://www.straitstimes.com/life/enter ... or-breasts</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question:<br />1. According to the news, Will Liu’s live stream attracts lots of fans in very short time. What’s the main reason of his success?<br />2. Do you ever learn sports with a coach and how is the experience? How do you think about following a coach on internet or TV program to exercise?<br />3. If you are sent into quarantine at home because of epidemic prevention, what will you do to go through it?<br />4. Is your exercising habit influenced by the pandemic? What is your solution?<br /><br /><br />Session II<br />Life in Taiwan: lunch box culture<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0RcpZ7vwSVg&amp;t=928s">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0RcpZ7vwSVg&amp;t=928s</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. As we can see in this video, foreigners are really interested and fascinated to boxed meal in Taiwan. Why it’s so popular in your opinion?<br />2. The Youtuber mentioned about C/P value of a boxed meal. According to the inflation, what’s the ideal price of a boxed meal now? Will you consider to buy a boxed meal around NT$200 or more?<br />3. Besides boxed meal, what kind of food style do you like and why?<br />4. Do you think Taiwanese boxed meal could be popular in global category? What’s your reason?...<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri May 13, 2022 5:29 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
